---
import { SITE_TITLE, FRIEND_LINKS } from '../consts';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div>
      <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-bold text-ink">
        <span class="grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-neon-cyan to-brand-600 text-[11px] font-black text-void">ib</span>
        {SITE_TITLE}
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
        关于 AI 的学习笔记与技术分享。记录提示词工程、大模型原理与 AI 工具实测，
        希望对同样在学习 AI 的你有帮助。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">热门主题</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/提示词/">提示词工程</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/大模型/">大模型</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/AI工具/">AI 工具</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/AI订阅/">AI 订阅</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">站点</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/blog/">全部文章</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/about/">关于本站</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/rss.xml">RSS 订阅</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">友情链接</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        {
          FRIEND_LINKS.map((link) => (
            <li>
              <a
                class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan"
                href={link.href}
                title={link.desc}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener external"
              >
                {link.name}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-white/5 py-6 text-center text-xs text-muted">
    © {year} {SITE_TITLE} · 内容仅供学习参考
  </div>
</footer>
